<br />
Stifle. Not only does it prevent casting, it also prevents all of those special attacks. So a strategy would be to keep mobs stunned/stifled as well as lower their power. Turn them into pussy cats!
<br />

<br />
I really had no idea that stifle stopped all special attacks until recently. With this new knowledge I've been able to tell a big difference in my groups.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
